
                            Claudia Shell Commands                             

File Operations ---------------------   Directory Operations -------------------

cat    Display file contents            ls      List directory contents  
touch  Create empty files               cd      Change directory
fstat  Show file information            pwd     Print working directory
rm     Remove files                     mkdir   Create directories


System Information ------------------   Shell Built-ins ------------------------

date   Display date/time                echo    Print text
id     Show user/group IDs              help    Show this help
pid    Show process ID                  exit    Exit shell


Development Tools -------------------   Miscellaneous --------------------------

lisp   Start Lisp interpreter           seek    Test file seeking



